text.tspan: Predicting Donations to an International Health Organization

flowRoot.flowPara: Watsi (www.watsi.org) posts photos and descriptions of people in poor countries who are in need of a medical treatment that they cannot afford. Each patient profile remains on the site until the patients treatment is fully funded by donors accessing the site. Using Pythons webpage parsing and machine-learning tools, I explore the determinants of donation rate. In particular, do patients who smile in their photo get funded more quickly?
